OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,FThe King has delivered his speech to
OL,7,FParliament, formally opening the new
OL,8,Fparliamentary year, as questions
OL,9,Fsurround the prime minister's future.
OL,11,FThe government is in turmoil after
OL,12,Flast week's disastrous election
OL,13,Flosses, leading Labour ministers and
OL,14,FMPs to call for Keir Starmer's
OL,15,Fresignation.
OL,17,FBut regardless of what's happening
OL,18,Fwith Labour, the business of the state
OL,19,Fcontinues, and on Wednesday, the King
OL,20,Funveiled what the government hopes to
OL,21,Flegislate in the coming months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,FHere's the King's speech to Parliament:
OL,8,F"An increasingly dangerous and
OL,9,Fvolatile world threatens the United
OL,10,FKingdom, with the conflict in the
OL,11,FMiddle East only the most recent
OL,12,Fexample. Every element of the nation's
OL,13,Fenergy, defence and economic security
OL,14,Fwill be tested.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will respond to this
OL,7,Fworld with strength and aim to create
OL,8,Fa country that is fair for all. My
OL,9,Fministers will take decisions that
OL,10,Fprotect the energy, defence and
OL,11,Feconomic security of the United
OL,12,FKingdom for the long-term.
OL,14,F"They will defend the British values
OL,15,Fof decency, tolerance and respect for
OL,16,Fdifference under our common flag, and
OL,17,Fthey will harness the potential of the
OL,18,Fpride felt across this country for its
OL,19,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will take urgent action
OL,7,Fto tackle antisemitism and ensure all
OL,8,Fcommunities feel safe.
OL,10,F"My Government believes that the
OL,11,FUnited Kingdom's economic security
OL,12,Fdepends on raising living standards in
OL,13,Fevery part of the United Kingdom. My
OL,14,FMinisters will support measures that
OL,15,Fmaintain stability and control the
OL,16,Fcost of living. They will use public
OL,17,Finvestment to shape markets and
OL,18,Fattract further private investment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"They will deploy the power of an
OL,7,Factive State in partnership with
OL,8,Fbusiness and enable reforms that
OL,9,Fsupport higher growth and a fair deal
OL,10,Ffor working people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government believes that improved
OL,7,Ftrading relations are vital for the
OL,8,FUnited Kingdom's economic security,
OL,9,Ffor significantly raising economic
OL,10,Fgrowth, and for lowering prices for
OL,11,Fworking people. My ministers will
OL,12,Fintroduce legislation to take
OL,13,Fadvantage of new trading
OL,14,Fopportunities, including a Bill to
OL,15,Fstrengthen ties with the European
OL,16,FUnion (European Partnership Bill).
OL,26,@xD@GpmxD@apn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will also support the
OL,7,Feconomic security of British
OL,8,Fbusinesses. Legislation will be
OL,9,Fintroduced to tackle late payments
OL,10,F(Small Business Protections (Late
OL,11,FPayments) Bill) and to reduce the
OL,12,Fburden of unnecessary regulation
OL,13,Fthrough innovation (Regulating for
OL,14,FGrowth Bill).
OL,26,@rD@ApmsD@OpnuD@TpmvD@Lpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"The United Kingdom's economic
OL,7,Fsecurity depends upon world-class
OL,8,Finfrastructure. Legislation will be
OL,9,Fintroduced to unlock the benefits of
OL,10,Fairport expansion (Civil Aviation
OL,11,FBill); enable roads to be built at
OL,12,Fpace, including the Lower Thames
OL,13,FCrossing (Highways (Financing) Bill);
OL,14,Fand deliver a fair deal for the North
OL,15,Fof England through Northern Powerhouse
OL,16,FRail (Northern Powerhouse Rail Bill).
OL,18,F"My Ministers will continue to take
OL,19,Fall action necessary to safeguard the
OL,20,Fdomestic production of steel (Steel
OL,21,FIndustry (Nationalisation) Bill).
OL,26,@rD@SpmsD@EpnuD@JpmuD@dpnxD@FpmxD@dpn|D@
OL,26,A^pm}D@`pn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will also improve the
OL,7,FUnited Kingdom's security by
OL,8,Fcontinuing to invest in the renewal of
OL,9,Fpublic services. My Ministers will
OL,10,Fpush forward with significant reforms
OL,11,Fto the police (Police Reform Bill),
OL,12,Fthe National Health Service (NHS
OL,13,FModernisation Bill), and to the
OL,14,Fcriminal justice system (Courts
OL,15,FModernisation Bill) to help them
OL,16,Fdeliver services the British people
OL,17,Fexpect.
OL,26,@sD@OpmsD@bpntD@]pmuD@SpnvD@YpmwD@Spn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"Legislation will be introduced to
OL,7,Fincrease confidence in the security of
OL,8,Fthe immigration and asylum systems
OL,9,F(Immigration and Asylum Bill).
OL,11,F"My Government will improve critical
OL,12,Finfrastructure with legislation to
OL,13,Fclean up the water industry (Clean
OL,14,FWater Bill) and establish Great
OL,15,FBritish Railways (Railways and
OL,16,FPassenger Benefits Bill).
OL,26,@qD@ApmqD@]pnuD@]pmvD@KpnwD@RpmxD@Xpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government believes that the
OL,7,FUnited Kingdom should be a country
OL,8,Ffair for all and a place where every
OL,9,Fchild is included in the nation's
OL,10,Fhighest aspirations. My Ministers
OL,11,Fbelieve that every child deserves the
OL,12,Fchance to succeed to the best of his
OL,13,For her ability and not be held back
OL,14,Fdue to poverty, special educational
OL,15,Fneeds, or a lack of respect for
OL,16,Fvocational education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Ministers will continue to invest
OL,7,Fin apprenticeships and measures that
OL,8,Ftackle youth unemployment. They will
OL,9,Frespond to the Milburn Review and the
OL,10,FTimms Review and continue to reform
OL,11,Fthe welfare system to support both
OL,12,Fyoung and disabled people to flourish
OL,13,Fin work as the basis for longterm
OL,14,Feconomic security.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"A Bill will be brought forward to
OL,7,Fraise standards in schools and
OL,8,Fintroduce generational reforms of the
OL,9,Fspecial educational needs system
OL,10,F(Education for All Bill). My Ministers
OL,11,Fwill also proceed with the
OL,12,Fintroduction of Digital ID that will
OL,13,Fmodernise how citizens interact with
OL,14,Fpublic services (Digital Access to
OL,15,FServices Bill).
OL,26,@rD@ApmrD@XpnvD@QpmwD@Npn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"Alongside strong public services and
OL,7,Fa strong economy, the highest
OL,8,Fstandards of trust in public office
OL,9,Fare essential for the social contract
OL,10,Fand the United Kingdom's collective
OL,11,Fsecurity. My Government will introduce
OL,12,Fthe Hillsborough Law to bring forward
OL,13,Fa duty of candour for public servants
OL,14,F(Public Office (Accountability) Bill).
OL,26,@vD@ApmvD@epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Ministers will also introduce
OL,7,Flegislation to enable peerages to be
OL,8,Fremoved (Removal of Peerages Bill). My
OL,9,FGovernment will bring forward
OL,10,Fproposals that strengthen the
OL,11,Fdelivery, accountability, innovation
OL,12,Fand productivity of the Civil Service.
OL,13,FThese proposals will also seek to
OL,14,Fsafeguard its impartiality and core
OL,15,Fvalues, to enhance trust and
OL,16,Fconfidence in the institutions of
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@pD@IpmpD@bpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will bring forward a
OL,7,FBill to speed up remediation for
OL,8,Fpeople living in homes with unsafe
OL,9,Fcladding (Remediation Bill) and a
OL,10,Fdraft Bill to ban abusive conversion
OL,11,Fpractices (Draft Conversion Practices
OL,12,FBill).
OL,14,F"In this volatile world, my Government
OL,15,Fwill continue to pursue foreign policy
OL,16,Fbased on a calm assessment of the
OL,17,Fnational interest. It will continue
OL,18,Fits unflinching support for the brave
OL,19,Fpeople of Ukraine, who fight on the
OL,20,Ffrontline of freedom.
OL,26,@qD@JpmqD@[pnsD@KpmtD@Epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Ministers will seek to improve
OL,7,Frelations with European partners as a
OL,8,Fvital step in strengthening European
OL,9,Fsecurity. It will continue to promote
OL,10,Flong term peace in the Middle East and
OL,11,Fthe Two-State solution in Israel and
OL,12,FPalestine.
OL,14,F"My Government will also uphold the
OL,15,FUnited Kingdom's unbreakable
OL,16,Fcommitment to NATO and our NATO
OL,17,Fallies, including through a sustained
OL,18,Fincrease in defence spending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"My Government will seek to reinforce
OL,12,Fthe long-term energy, defence and
OL,13,Feconomic security of the United
OL,14,FKingdom as an essential component of
OL,15,Fstrength on the world stage. This will
OL,16,Finclude housing, which can be a source
OL,17,Fof insecurity for many people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Ministers will bring forward
OL,7,Flegislation to increase long-term
OL,8,Finvestment in social housing (Social
OL,9,FHousing Renewal Bill) and to reform
OL,10,Fthe leasehold system, including the
OL,11,Fcapping of ground rents (Commonhold
OL,12,Fand Leasehold Reform Bill).
OL,26,@pD@^pmqD@UpnsD@YpmtD@Zpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31720
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will introduce
OL,7,Flegislation to tackle the growing
OL,8,Fthreat from foreign state entities and
OL,9,Ftheir proxies (Tackling State Threats
OL,10,FBill). They will respond to the
OL,11,Fhorrific attack in Southport with
OL,12,Fmeasures to protect the British people
OL,13,Ffrom extreme violence, and honour the
OL,14,Fvictims, the injured and their
OL,15,Ffamilies (National Security Bill).
OL,17,F"My Ministers will also introduce
OL,18,Flegislation to improve the country's
OL,19,Fdefences against cyber-security
OL,20,Fthreats (Cyber Security and Resilience
OL,21,FBill).
OL,26,@qD@OpmrD@EpnwD@JpmwD@apn|D@Ipm}D@Epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31721
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will support our
OL,7,Fgallant Armed Forces and their
OL,8,Ffamilies who make considerable
OL,9,Fpersonal sacrifices for the collective
OL,10,Fsecurity and freedom of everyone in
OL,11,Fthe United Kingdom. My Ministers will
OL,12,Frecognise this service with an Armed
OL,13,FForces Bill that improves the service
OL,14,Fjustice system and establishes the
OL,15,FArmed Forces covenant in statute
OL,16,F(Armed Forces Bill).
OL,26,@xD@ApmxD@Spn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/26
