OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Ministers believe that energy
OL,7,Findependence must be a long-term goal
OL,8,Fof national security and that the
OL,9,Fnation's energy security requires long-
OL,10,Fterm investment and reform, as
OL,11,Fdemonstrated by recent events in the
OL,12,FMiddle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31723
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"Increased production of clean British
OL,7,Fenergy will help to ensure that
OL,8,Fenemies of the United Kingdom cannot
OL,9,Fattack the economic security of the
OL,10,FBritish people. My Ministers will
OL,11,Ftherefore introduce an Energy
OL,12,FIndependence Bill to scale-up
OL,13,Fhomegrown renewable energy and protect
OL,14,Fliving standards for the long-term
OL,15,F(Energy Independence Bill).
OL,17,F"My Ministers will also take forward
OL,18,Frecommendations of the Nuclear
OL,19,FRegulatory Review and encourage a new
OL,20,Fera of British nuclear energy
OL,21,Fgeneration (Nuclear Regulation Bill).
OL,26,@wD@ApmwD@Zpn}D@Lpm}D@dpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31724
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"My Government will remain a leading
OL,7,Fadvocate for tackling climate change
OL,8,Fand achieving a world free from
OL,9,Fpoverty. The United Kingdom will also
OL,10,Ftake action to reduce humanitarian
OL,11,Fneed and conflict around the world.
OL,13,F"My Ministers will champion the rights
OL,14,Fof women and girls to live in a world
OL,15,Ffree from violence. This will include
OL,16,Fpromoting women's full economic and
OL,17,Fpolitical participation within their
OL,18,Fsocieties, with agency over the
OL,19,Fdecisions that impact their lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
