OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778702756
OL,3,CIn full: The King's speech to
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"Next year, the United Kingdom will
OL,7,Ftake on the G20 Presidency and host
OL,8,Fthe G20 Summit to drive global growth
OL,9,Fand reinforce global stability, which
OL,10,Fis essential for the prosperity of
OL,11,Fworking people across the country.
OL,13,F"My Government is committed to the
OL,14,Fstrength and integrity of the Union of
OL,15,Fthe United Kingdom and will continue
OL,16,Fto work closely with the devolved
OL,17,Fgovernments to deliver for citizens
OL,18,Facross the whole of the nation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/26
